Value Required LOCAL_IFACE (\S+)
Value CHASSIS_ID ([0-9a-fA-F:\.]+)
Value PORT_ID (.+)
Value SYSTEM_NAME (.+)

Start
  ^>>>>\s+Local Interface\s*:\s*${LOCAL_IFACE}\s*<<<<
  ^Chassis ID\s{2,}:\s*${CHASSIS_ID}
  ^Port ID\s{2,}:\s*${PORT_ID}
  ^System Name\s{2,}:\s*${SYSTEM_NAME}
  ^-{10,} -> Record
  ^__TEXTFSM_EOF__ -> Record
  ^. -> Continue
